ScreenView – Themes & Widgets
Description
Give your Lock & Home screens a complete makeover with stylish wallpapers, trendy themes, handy widgets, and top screen packs!
Dive deep and try Depth Effect Wallpapers for iOS 16 with ScreenView!
Style up your screen with Shuffle Wallpapers for iOS 16!
Mobile devices have revolutionized our lives and become essential in our daily activities. We strive to make everyone’s screen time more enjoyable and eye-pleasing with a full range of customization options. We made it our goal to help you beautify your Home & Lock screens to match your personality and let you stand out from the crowd.
For complete access to all Wallpapers, Themes & Widgets, you will need to allow access to the following:
• Photos - to import backgrounds you like and set them to your Lock Screen;
• Notifications to keep you informed when new wallpapers are added to the app.
Features:
4K Live Wallpapers
Create a smooth blurred background easily using our blur tool
Create Notchless background easily using our notchless tool
Easy navigation: check out the Grid Mode to browse fast and the latest arrivals or take a look at all recent uploaded wallpapers
Liven up your Apple Watch with beautiful watch faces
Widgets for Home & Lock screens
Technology
Swift 5.3
Swift on server